      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Non-Jury Trials Justice and Security (Northern Ireland) Act 2007
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Extending non-jury trial provisions under the Justice and Security (Northern
Ireland) Act 2007 (“the 2007 Act”) requires secondary legislation which must
be approved by both Houses of Parliament. The Government recognises the
need to keep the public informed and to allow people the opportunity to
comment on policy proposals.</p>

  </div>
</div>

